First 5 minutes of hosting beta I didnt want to anymore. [size=18pt]COMMENT WHAT I CAN DO TO MAKE THIS BETTER- BUT DONT FLAME[/size]
This took some time to do so comment your opinion but please dont flame.
Credits to: Me Bainscape for some ideas and animations Evolution X for base
PICS [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/if29p3.png[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/15ddt2.png[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/1z7q8p.png[/img] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/fn5qo7.png[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/2uoga2x.png[/img] [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/2yki8t1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/dptje1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/27z9r15.png[/img] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/2rz9xxt.png[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/34sk01j.png[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/2z5u4o4.png[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/182887.png[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/152hyxk.png[/img]
Downloads
Client: http://www.mediafire.com/?svkuycb272nu8b2
Server: http://www.mediafire.com/?dwmtykml2xl
How to change the client to connect to your ip: Go into the client folder and look for gui.java Hit ctrl+F and search serverip Change the ip to 0.0.0.0 Save and compile
I will upload a client that connects to localhost in a minute I just remembered it wasnt on that.
There will probably be a V4 that will have bounty hunter, duel arena, and some other minigames. V4 will not be coming out anytime soon because i quit making rsps. Im back into real runescape.
[size=14pt]COMMENT WHAT I CAN DO TO MAKE IT BETTER[/size] [size=14pt]IF YOU DONT LIKE CUSTOMS THEN DONT USE THEM[/size]
